atoms.title: Before You Start
atoms.text:
### Introduction
In this lesson, we will focus on the questioning part of the QMV process in more depth.

Mose specifically, we will teach you how to examine data, identify what elements of it are most significant to investigate a hypothesis, and quantify the impact of data quality on their model. 

### Downloads
This [download link](https://www.udacity.com/api/nodes/3606578599/supplemental_media/lesson-2zip/download) contains the files that you need to follow along Don in lesson 2.
